snippet.title: Intelligence I - vc4000
snippet.description: This cassette for the Interton VC 4000 is a collection of labyrinth games. There are different modes to test even the most skilled labyrinth solver. Blogpost: http://retro-spill.blogspot.com/2014/03/intelligence-i-9-vc-4000.html
